story_arceus_08_08000/2401_1101_0100_20: For the first match in block A...
story_arceus_08_08000/2401_1101_0200_20:
The rock-solid Pokémon Trainer, Brock,
is ready to rock!
story_arceus_08_08000/2401_1101_0300_20:
He’s up against the fighting farmer!
Here’s the Grass-type expert, Milo!
story_arceus_08_08000/2401_1101_0400_20:
And now, introducing the first match of
block B!
story_arceus_08_08000/2401_1101_0500_20:
The Tomboyish Mermaid, Misty, takes
the stage!
story_arceus_08_08000/2401_1101_0600_20:
Her opponent is...the raging wave!
The master of Water types, Nessa!
story_arceus_08_08000/2401_1001_0700_10:
I’m giving this all I’ve got—even against
you, Nessa!
story_arceus_08_08000/2401_1001_0800_10:
Of course! I won’t forgive you if you go
easy on me!
story_arceus_08_08000/2401_1001_0900_10: I look forward to battling you, Brock!
story_arceus_08_08000/2401_1001_1000_10:
I won’t hold back in this Gym Leader
showdown!
story_arceus_08_08000/2401_1001_1200_10:
No matter how serious you are, we can
take anything you throw at us!
story_arceus_08_08000/2401_1101_1300_20: And now, let the first match...begin!
story_arceus_08_08000/2401_1001_1500_10:
Wow! Onix is supposed to be weak to
Grass-type attacks. I didn’t think it’d
withstand so much!
story_arceus_08_08000/2401_1001_1600_10: I’m impressed! You’re tough as weeds!
story_arceus_08_08000/2401_1001_1900_10:
Oof! At this rate, Eldegoss, our attacks won’t
be enough to finish them off!
story_arceus_08_08000/2401_1001_2100_10:
It’s Dynamax time! They’re about to be
uprooted!
story_arceus_08_08000/2401_1001_2400_10: We won’t be washed away so easily!
story_arceus_08_08000/2401_1001_2500_10: Starmie! Let’s pick up the pace!
story_arceus_08_08000/2401_1001_2700_10: I hope you can take this!
story_arceus_08_08000/2401_1001_3000_10:
Tighten up your defense, Onix! We’ll get
through this if you can hold strong!
story_arceus_08_08000/2401_1001_3100_10:
What? I can’t believe that didn’t
uproot them!
story_arceus_08_08000/2401_1001_3200_10: Well done! Good job staying strong!
story_arceus_08_08000/2401_1001_3400_10:
You defeated us fair and square, Brock!
Good luck at the semifinals!
story_arceus_08_08000/2401_1001_3500_10: Thanks! I’ll be fighting for your sake, too!
story_arceus_08_08000/2401_1001_3600_10: Phew! I can’t believe we dodged that!
story_arceus_08_08000/2401_1001_3700_10:
Our turn! Let’s go, Starmie! We’re going on
an all-out offensive!
story_arceus_08_08000/2401_1001_3800_10:
Your surging might overpowered ours!
Keep it up, and good luck in the next match!
story_arceus_08_08000/2401_1001_3900_10: Thanks! We’ll be sure to shine at the top!
